{"tid":2316167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大多間學生會譴責校方主動報警舉報畢業生","createTime":"2020-12-07T16:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T23:03:56.000Z","uid":66324,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed4eabd7c9109653435ba5e35b6a75db6ade55f","tid":2316167,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564075-20201208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564075-20201208.htm&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7PZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=eb00c8ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564075-20201208.htm&h=a703ba8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564075-20201208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"440d007388c62ab06e5ac49110739d3eab660b8c","tid":2316167,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"中大學生會臨時行政委員會聯同中大多間書院的學生會發聲明，強烈譴責中大校方在上月畢業生遊行之後，主動報警舉報畢業生。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，中大校方高層在去年中大校園衝突中，前往現場探望學生，並與警方談判，為中大贏得一時美譽。但一年過去，中大對於在校園內疾呼對香港未來願景的畢業生予以譴責，甚至報警處理，批評校方打壓校園內的自由，一手瓦解學生與校方之間的互信，丟棄作為最高等學府的一切辦學理念。<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕8人，指他們涉嫌在上月19日、即中大畢業禮當日，在中大校園內參與未經批准集結，部分人同時涉嫌觸犯煽動分裂國家罪。"},{"pid":"04377c19f0480bbf2662b4f808d4dba63f2ecea1","tid":2316167,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e9c8516592e33d22894ea48d0dd66a9796866","tid":2316167,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"中大果隻保安主管<br />\n係被革走既黑警<br />\n搞鳩手足一定落足力"},{"pid":"15a938d56c8ec423d892a944a41fd0bded5d0600","tid":2316167,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"